{"tid":775031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家先發現 原來香港啲女咁難溝","createTime":"2018-08-10T19:51:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T01:28:49.000Z","uid":88689,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fab3058fbe62cf1706c59f76f4d2f43af22bf853","tid":775031,"uid":88689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T19:51:57.000Z","msg":"適逢聽日周末 諗住落尖沙咀飲野識女<br />\n<br />\n平時都冇乜留意<br />\n因為次次渣開車泊門口附近<br />\n落車係門口枱坐果啲女都好易傾到計有下文<br />\n<br />\n你老味今日留左車匙係自己公司又唔想返去拎<br />\n選擇搭地鐵 聽曰先返去拎<br />\n結果啲女傾一兩句就唔太想理我<br />\n自問普通樣 但啲女寧願揀個矮肥<br />\n渣埋架爛鬼BMW 325<br />\n<br />\n冇車冇樓原來真係咁難溝女<br />\n到而家都冇著落 我決定返去拎車 <br />\n然後返黎特登買兩包薯片走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638d75328b7e8a978ebf96aa2deb79e0fe3080d3","tid":775031,"uid":195561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb245d646b2f399b438ccb8609d705c279f61e5e","tid":775031,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:28:49.000Z","msg":"貨van<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}